data.description: Welcome home to Imperial Cove--the extremely popular + impeccably maintained 55+ gated community featuring a beautiful clubhouse with ALL the amenities located on the shores of Tampa Bay and minutes to major retail (Costco, Target, Lowe's, Home Depot and more). Enjoy the Florida-friendly lifestyle from your 2 bedroom, 2 bath end unit villa with covered carport parking + private storage closet. Move right in to this lovely east-facing home with beautiful morning sunshine through the big bay window in lovely, modernized eat-in kitchen featuring warm wood cabinetry, solid surface countertops, tile flooring, pantry shelving + pantry closet. Split bedroom floorplan features two very ample bedrooms with Master at the rear of the home + walk-in closet. Spacious dining and living room combination is great for entertaining family + friends and also adjoins back sunroom overlooking a lovely green space. Walk right out the back door to your car for convenient loading and unloading. Interior laundry room includes washer/dryer, 2014 water heater. BRAND NEW 2020 A/C system will keep you cool as a clam. Check out the swimming pool, exercise facilities, fishing pier, outdoor grills, shuffleboard, putting greens, billiards, card room, ballroom and more! Take State Road 60 west straight to Clearwater Beach or east to Tampa airport. This community is a hidden gem in a very convenient, central location. Sorry, NO PETS, NO MOTORCYLES.
